Food.name: Cheesecake Burger
Food.description: The classic fullstack with a vegetable garden on top
Food.comments: My oh my, that is one thick patty!

Food.name: Five Guys Burger
Food.description: Classic cheeseburger, yet worth half your rent
Food.comments: It really takes five guys to make one burger?

Food.name: Applebees Burger
Food.description: Picture worthy, but not taste worthy
Food.comments: Who would've thought a bun could have smoother skin than mine?

Food.name: Red Robin Burger
Food.description: Has all the daily nutrients you need under one bun!
Food.comments: Good, but easy on the lettuce, feels like I'm eating an iceberg

Food.name: Shakeshack Burger
Food.description: Don't compare us to In-n-Out, we take that as an insult
Food.comments: They really shack up the burger the way you want

Food.name: Steak n Shake
Food.description: Steak and cheese in between buns, I'd like 3 please
Food.comments: Very meaty meat, very cheesy cheese, and the pickles just top it off

Food.name: Wendys
Food.description: You won't need to eat the rest of the day after getting lunch with us
Food.comments: Dorothy had red slippers, Wendy had red hair AND stacked burgers

Food.name: Whataburger
Food.description: You'll really see why they say everything is bigger and better in Texas!
Food.comments: Ask for the WhataSize........ your life will change forever!!
